<span style="font-weight:normal;">Recommendation for improvement</span>
*Make use of CL and DDs with<span style="font-weight:normal;"> </span>[http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/WG42_(Wurfger%C3%A4t_42) WG42 (Wurfgerät 42)] and [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Special_Type_2_Amphibious_Tank Special Type 2 Amphibious Tank] and upgrade it to 10 star if possible for 3x firepower to reach cap damages at night.
*Better to have FBB with higher firepower in escort as the damage formula for [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Type_3_Shell Type 3 Shell] is by multiplying the firepower with 2.5, which mean chuuhaed FBB still got a shot to kill. For example, Iowa.
*Since the boss escorts usually get knockout before the main fleet can get a chance to shell, it is better to just equip all carriers with torpedo bombers (blue) then having some with divebombers (red) to attack bosses.
*Better go for AS+ with more fighters to reduce bauxite cost and lower the enemy bombers strength in opening strike in D and G. AS+ also increase your contact rate to further boost your acc, critical damage and eva from the enemy.
*High ranking double chevron LBAS bomber can helps in killing off the escort for main to focus on himes. You may even send all LBAS to Boss node to have more change of clearing the map if you lack proper ships and equipment, but in exchange for less chance to kill off BB hime twins before they get to fire another round of reck.
*Set Fighter in LBAS are great to reduce the lost of rank. Some Interceptor fighters can also be used for shorter node.
*Ignore FCF during Last Dance for AS+, since in my case it rarely activate as Akizuki often get shohaed while losing a AACI DD in boss node usually make ships reck easily and more chance for boss to Chuhaed/Taihaed the main killer before Night battle. But unless AS+ already achieved, FCF maybe consider.
*Most CA(V) can't produce good damage as FBB on boss most of the time especially Hard mode Last dance when the Boss had 214 armor while the chance for getting chuuhaed is very high. Might as well replace it with Maya with AACI set up and bring in a high level and firepower DD with installation set up to replace a AACI setup DD. But, there is suggestion of using CAV (Tone class) with 2 Guns, [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/WG42_(Wurfger%C3%A4t_42) WG42 (Wurfgerät 42)] and [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Type_3_Shell Type 3 Shell] setup by replacing DA in day battle for Big damage at night to reach cap damage.
*Set 3rd LBAS base into interceptor fighter to reduce bauxite lose when farming.
*As for support expedition, support shelling seem to be better than arial support with more chance to kill off escort while saving bauxites, need more testing.
*<span style="font-weight:normal;">Never test fleet composite in Hard mode (Lesson learned TT_TT)</span>
*Hayasui in escort with [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Special_Type_2_Amphibious_Tank Special Type 2 Amphibious Tank] can be fun and have any kind of ship you like to join the fleet, Yamato ect.
*For those who want to exchange more torpedo bomber for opening air strike, adding akatsumaru for fighters would be a great choice, check [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/User:IElements IElements]'s [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Talk:Summer_2016_Event/@comment-IElements-20160818053122 comment] and [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/User:Arucart123 Arucart123]'s [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Talk:Summer_2016_Event/@comment-Allen92-20160819082238/@comment-Arucart123-20160819090611 comment]  for more information. [4][5]
*There is [http://ja.kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/%E3%82%B9%E3%83%AC%E3%83%83%E3%83%89:718 report of data in jp forum] found the debuff reduce -23 armor of Summer BBhime and Summer Seaporthime. Hence do it and send more LBASs, planes strike, gun, CI and whatever to kill them. [6]
